{
  "stem": "2718.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, we-- my parents choose-- have chosen to put me into public school for-- for primary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, in primary school, we-- it was-- it was most common.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't think that there was nothing personal about it, because I think it was aimed at every Jewish student, that they called us-- called us dirty Jews and stinky Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and it-- this-- this was the classmates, and not everyone of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of them were very good friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At the same time, the teachers certainly did-- did not discourage them to-- to upset us or to insult us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If there was such a-- such a teacher, well, I think he kept very much to himself and didn't show it in the public because he wouldn't have been very popular.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at that-- at that time, which was 1935, 1936, there was no real-- no real hateful anti-Semitism in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was not such a thing as anybody being hurt bodily in a school, no more than a usual fistfight or something between boys, which happens in any school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Doesn't matter what-- what public school, private school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't think there was-- who-- I was-- it would be more exaggerated if I would say it was a-- it-- it wasn't anything serious, put it this way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Wasn't anything serious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not in 1936, '37, certainly not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we play-- we play soccer in-- in teams against other schools, and like the same is-- the same is here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever went to a soccer match here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But whenever there's a-- there was [INAUDIBLE] playing, even the players who were not Jewish, they were called dirty Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and other teams were running them down and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was no different there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
